text: Skyler Joy (born November 14, 1999) also known by his ring name, Skitz, is an American professional wrestler. He is signed to Boca Raton Championship Wrestling. Joy has made appearances for Coastal Championship Wrestling and Wisconsin Professional Wrestling. He was born and raised in Menasha, Wisconsin. He was trained at the Dojo of Pain wrestling academy at the age of 16.
